            Specifies whether data disk should be deleted or detached upon VM
            deletion. Possible values are: **Delete.** If this value is used, the
            data disk is deleted when VM is deleted. **Detach.** If this value is
            used, the data disk is retained after VM is deleted. The default value
            is set to **Detach**.
